 Host 192.168.0.89 appears to be up.
 MAC Address: 08:00:69:08:AA:DC (Silicon Graphics)
 Nmap done: 256 IP addresses (2 hosts up) scanned in 28.933 seconds
Por defecto, IRIX viene con muchos servicios abiertos.
 # nmap 192.168.0.89
 
